<div class="container printable">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>{{ fullName }}</h1>
    <p>
    Email: <a href="mailto:{{ email }}">{{ email }}</a> | Phone:
    <a href="tel:{{ phoneNumber }}"
       >{{ phoneNumber | mask_phone_number }}</a
     >
     <br />
     {% if website %} Website: <a href="{{ website }}">{{ website }}</a> |
     {% endif %} {% if github %} GitHub:
     <a href="{{ github }}">{{ github }}</a> | {% endif %} {% if linkedin
     %} LinkedIn: <a href="{{ linkedin }}">{{ linkedin }}</a>
     {% endif %}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>{{ job_title }}</h2>
    <p>
    Date: {{ "" | get_formatted_today }}<br />
    Dear {{ salutation_name }},
    </p>

    <p>
    I hope this message finds you well. I am writing to express my strong
    interest in the position of {{ job_title }} as advertised. With high
    skill in {{ main_technologies | join(", ") }}, I believe I am well-positioned to
    contribute to your companyâ€™s success.
    </p>

    <p>
    Here are a few reasons why I believe I would be a great fit for the
    role:
    </p>

    <ul class="bullet-points">
      {% for bullet_point in bullet_points %}
      <li>{{ bullet_point }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    {% if closing_statement %}
    <p>{{ closing_statement }}</p>
    {% else %}
    <p>
    I am confident that my background in software development, combined
    with my passion for innovative technology, makes me a strong candidate
    for this role. I look forward to the opportunity to further discuss
    how I can contribute to your team and help achieve your goals.
    </p>
    {% endif %}

    <p class="signature">
    Best wishes,<br />
    <span class="name">{{ fullName }}</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
